2. **AgentList.test.tsx** - Added missing required properties (`orgId`, `capabilities`, `email` for associatedUser) to mock Agent objects; removed unused imports

3. **Auth test files** (ProtectedRoute.test.tsx, LoginForm.test.tsx, RegisterForm.test.tsx):
