5. **JobList.test.tsx** - Fixed PrintJob mocks (added required `userId`, `orgId`, `settings`; used `undefined` instead of `null` for optional fields; created full Printer objects)

6. **handlers.ts** - Fixed type assertions for request.json(); removed unused variables

